RELEASE NOTES
Cast of the Seven Godsends harks back to the days when classic
2D, run 'n gun, action-shooter games ruled the arcades. Four
levels of difficulty, six worlds to conquer, twelve mid and
end-of-level bosses, seven god-like armour sets, five basic
weapons and thirty-five magic combat spells
